\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(3) The decision of the Constitutional Court on the constitutionality of a legal sentence has the force of law. The decision formula is to be published in the law gazette.}
