(1) In the course of the next year, the Minister of Finance has to report to the People's Chamber about all budget receipts of an accounting year as well as about their use and the debts of the Federation in order to relieve the government. Evidence of assets must be attached to the invoice.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(2) The audit of the budget as well as the efficiency and correctness of the budget and economic management is carried out by the Federal Audit Office. Its members have judicial independence. Article 65 Paragraph 2 sentence 2 applies accordingly. He has to report annually to the government, the people's chamber and the state chamber on the results of his work.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
