(1) After this Constitution has come into force, the laws will be passed exclusively by the legislative bodies of the Federation and the L\u228\'3fnder provided for in this Constitution.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
(2) The law of the German Democratic Republic continues to apply as federal law, the subject matter of which does not fall within the exclusive legislative power of the states.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\cf0\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af6\afs24\alang1081\loch\f3\hich\af3\fs24\lang1049{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
